<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>PDF Result Template</title>
    <style>
        .logo {
            height: 130px;
            width: 170px;
        }

        .space {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .img-container {
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }

        .headings {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .headingRight {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .Container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .Footer {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .dotted {
            border-bottom: 2px dashed #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="Container">
        <span class="img-container">
            <img class="logo" src="{{ LogoPath }}" alt="" />
        </span>
        <h2 class="headings">FOURTH SCHEDULE</h2>
        <H3 class="headings">PART 1</H3>
        <H3 class="headings">FORMS FOR REVIEWS</H3>
        <H4 class="headingRight"> FORM RB 1</H4>
        <H3 class="headings">REPUBLIC OF KENYA</H3>
        <H3 class="headings">PUBLIC PROCUREMENT ADMINISTRATIVE REVIEW BOARD</H3>
        <H4 class="headings">APPLICATION NO <span class="dotted">{{ Applicationno }}</span></H4>
        <H4 class="headings">BETWEEN</H4>

        <H4 class="headings">
            <span class="dotted">{{ ApplicantName }}</span> APPLICANT</H4>
        <H4 class="headings"> AND</H4>
        <H4 class="headings">
            <span class="dotted">{{ PEName }}</span> RESPONDENT (<i>Procuring Entity or Director General</i>)
        </H4>
        <P class="space">Request for review of the decision of the <span class="dotted">{{
          PEName
        }}</span>
            (<i> Procuring Entity or Director General</i>) dated
            <span class="dotted">{{ ApplicationDate }} </span> in the matter of
            Tender No
            <span class="dotted">{{ TenderNo }}. </span>
        </P>
        <H3 class="headings">REQUEST FOR REVIEW</H3>
        <p class="space">
            I/We <span class="dotted">{{ ApplicantName }}</span>,the above named Applicant(s) of address:
            <span class="dotted">{{ PysicalAddress }} </span>.Fax No
            <span class="dotted">{{ Fax }}</span> ,Tel No
            <span class="dotted">{{ Telephone }}</span> ,Email
            <span class="dotted">{{ Email }}</span>, hereby request the Public Procurement Administrative Review Board
            to
            review the whole/part of the above mentioned decision on the following
            grounds,namely:-
        </p>
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            {{#each Grounds}}
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <p>{{ GroundNO }}.</p>
                </td>
                <td>{{{ Description }}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </table>
        <P class="space">By the memorandum,the Applicant request the Board for an Order/orders that:-</P>
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            {{#each Request}}
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <p>{{ GroundNO }}.</p>
                </td>
                <td>{{{ Description }}}</td>
            </tr>

            {{/each}}
        </table>
        <p>SIGNED <br></br>

            (Applicant).</p>
        <p>
            Dated on <span class="dotted">{{ ApplicationDate }} </span>
        </p>
        <hr style="height:2px;border:none;color:#333;background-color:#333;" />
        <h3>FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY</h3>
        <p class="space">
            Lodged with the secretary Public Procurement Administrative Review Board
            on
            <span class="dotted">{{ ReceivedDate }}. </span>
        </p>
        <br />

        <h3>SIGNED</h3>
        <h3>Board Secretary</h3>
    </div>
</body>

</html>